ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Labour of ALEXANDER WERZBERGER of Outremont, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Michel Bérubé, whose term has expired.
